|               |     Projection: promotional_sales.promotions, all_sales.total, CAST(promotional_sales.promotions AS Decimal128(15, 4)) / CAST(all_sales.total AS Decimal128(15, 4)) * Int64(100)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
